descriptionNullable:
A dataset containing 30,000 high-quality celebrity faces, resampled to 256px.
This dataset was used by NVIDIA in the research paper [Progressive Growing of GANs for Improved Quality, Stability, and Variation](https://arxiv.org/abs/1710.10196).
It is meant for generative models. As such, it only has images and no attributes/labels.
title: CelebA-HQ resized (256x256)
subtitle: The CelebA-HQ celebrity faces dataset
